<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١٠٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">دِينَارٍ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">سَمِعْتُ ابْنَ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(الضَّبُّ لَسْتُ آكُلُهُ وَلَا أُحَرِّمُهُ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
